{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://Vinnl.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"beans on toast (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Beans_on_toast\" title=\"Beans on toast\">beans on toast</a></b> <i>(example pictured)</i> have variously been referred to as \"skinheads\", \"skins on a raft\" and \"cowboy's dinner\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beans_on_toast","retrieved":1782204165613},{"title":"Licia Fertz (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Licia_Fertz\" title=\"Licia Fertz\">Licia Fertz</a></b> posed nude for <i>Rolling Stone</i> at the age of 89?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Licia_Fertz","retrieved":1782204165614},{"title":"Your Own Quiz (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the author of <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Your_Own_Quiz\" title=\"Your Own Quiz\">Your Own Quiz</a></b></i> wanted the readers to answer at least one question in the novel correctly at the same time as the main character?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Your_Own_Quiz","retrieved":1782204165614},{"title":"all three sons of Queen Elizabeth II and Prince Philip (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Descendants_of_Elizabeth_II\" title=\"Descendants of Elizabeth II\">all three sons of Queen Elizabeth&nbsp;II and Prince Philip</a></b> attended <a href=\"/wiki/Gordonstoun\" title=\"Gordonstoun\">Gordonstoun School</a>?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Descendants_of_Elizabeth_II","retrieved":1782204165616},{"title":"44 West 77th Street (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that one writer described the decorations of <b><a href=\"/wiki/44_West_77th_Street\" title=\"44 West 77th Street\">44&nbsp;West 77th Street</a></b> as having seemingly been \"squeezed out of a pastry tube\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/44_West_77th_Street","retrieved":1782204165617},{"title":"Kino-Eye (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the documentary film <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Kino-Eye_(film)\" title=\"Kino-Eye (film)\">Kino-Eye</a></b></i> includes footage reversed by director <a href=\"/wiki/Dziga_Vertov\" title=\"Dziga Vertov\">Dziga Vertov</a> to show bread being unmade and a bull being \"resurrected\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kino-Eye_(film)","retrieved":1782204165618},{"title":"Patrick Castagno (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Patrick_Castagno\" title=\"Patrick Castagno\">Patrick Castagno</a></b> won his 60th state championship shortly after his 60th birthday?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patrick_Castagno","retrieved":1782204165620},{"title":"Gordon House (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the <b><a href=\"/wiki/Gordon_House_(Amherstburg)\" title=\"Gordon House (Amherstburg)\">Gordon House</a></b> was the headquarters of a project to rebuild an 1813 ship?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gordon_House_(Amherstburg)","retrieved":1782204165621},{"title":"Vasily Baranshchikov (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Vasily_Baranshchikov\" title=\"Vasily Baranshchikov\">Vasily Baranshchikov</a></b><span class=\"nowrap\">'s</span> travelogue was an 18th-century bestseller, despite what one contemporary review deemed sloppy writing and an ungrateful, whiny tone?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vasily_Baranshchikov","retrieved":1782204165623},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<span class=\"mw-empty-elt\" about=\"#mwt8\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\" id=\"mwIQ\" data-mw=\"{&quot;parts&quot;:[{&quot;template&quot;:{&quot;target&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;banner&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:&quot;./Template:Banner&quot;},&quot;params&quot;:{&quot;direction&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;left&quot;},&quot;title&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;Galway&quot;},&quot;type&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;dotm&quot;},&quot;image&quot;:{&quot;wt&quot;:&quot;GalwayBanner1.jpg&quot;},&qu